  'enter_the_organisations_iati_organisation_identifier'                                  => 'es_ Enter the organisation\'s IATI organisation identifier. If you cannot provide an identifier then you must provide the name of the organisation.<br><br><a target=\'_blank\' href=\'https://iatistandard.org/en/guidance/publishing-data/data-quality-and-visualisation/finding-other-organisations-identifiers/\'>Click here for information on how to find other organisations\' identifiers</a>.',
  'the_type_of_aid_being_supplied_project_type_intervention'                              => 'es_ The type of aid being supplied (project-type intervention, budget support, debt relief, etc.). This default will be applied to all new activities. It can be overridden for individual activities if needed. <br><br><a target=\'_blank\' href=\'https://iatistandard.org/en/iati-standard/203/codelists/aidtype/\'>Click here for more information</a>',
  'what_is_an_activity_description'                                                       => 'es_ For IATI, you provide information on your organisation\'s development and humanitarian \'activities\'. Activities can be programmes, projects, or any unit of work that makes sense for your organisation.',
